column5: Just a thread for people to post when they are going to rainy lake and what species they plan to target!
Will be there, but not unitl October 1st. Plan to target walleye for the most part
going to Rainy May 23rd if the ice is gone. Actually going up anyway,but sure hope we aren't stranded on shore.
Second week of June for Walleyes
3rd week of June for a houseboat trip, walleyes for sure, crappies if I can get a little help from members here....please....

I have 3rd week in August booked at Thunderbird. I alsso plan to go around the 3rd week in June but won't ook that till my brother in law let'ss me know his schedule. Might also run up for a few days end of May if the weather is good.
